## TagType type

Type that enumerates the allowed types of HTML elements in the document header.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type TagType =
  | "base"
  | "link"
  | "style"
  | "meta"
  | "script"
  | "noscript"
  | "template";
```
